sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Facade
    participant UserModel
    participant Storage

    Client->>API: POST /users (name, email, password)
    API->>Facade: register_user(data)
    Facade->>UserModel: new User(data)
    UserModel-->>Facade: User instance
    Facade->>Storage: save(User)
    Storage-->>Facade: success
    Facade-->>API: return 201 Created
    API-->>Client: HTTP 201 Created
